data.instruction:
Call the free Hacker News Algolia API to find top stories and Ask HN posts about the topic. HN is free — no payment needed.

Story search: GET https://hn.algolia.com/api/v1/search?tags=story&hitsPerPage=20&query={TOPIC_URL_ENCODED}
Ask HN search: GET https://hn.algolia.com/api/v1/search?tags=ask_hn&hitsPerPage=10&query={TOPIC_URL_ENCODED}

Keep only items with points ≥ 10. For each: points, num_comments, title, objectID (use as ID for seen-log).
HN URL format: https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id={objectID}

Sort by points descending. Return top 15 stories + top 5 Ask HN posts.
